com.tomtom.cpp.select.api.query

Class TableBoundSelect<R extends Record,T extends Entity<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomtom.cpp.select.api.query.TableBoundSelect<R,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - record type
    T - entity

    public class TableBoundSelect<R extends Record,T extends Entity<?>>
extends java.lang.Object
    The TableBoundSelect class is the starting point for building the query. This class is tied to a specific entity that you specify at the beginning. This class is used to define what will be "select"-ed from the given entity.
